metadata.name: Woman. Born in the USSR
metadata.description:
In the first decades of the Soviet era, this was how it happened - a female hero was supposed to appear next to a male hero. 
All photos in this collection are dedicated to the Soviet Union. They are made on the old large format camera 1870-1890s using wet collodion.
Scan of the image created by the technology of the 19th century with silver on the glass. 
Size 13*18 cm. 
Created: December 2021. Moscow.
